Mortality in children with cerebral palsy in rural Bangladesh: a 
population-based surveillance study.

Jahan I(1)(2), Karim T(1)(2)(3), Das MC(1)(2), Muhit M(1)(2), Mcintyre S(4), 
Smithers-Sheedy H(3)(4), Badawi N(3)(4), Khandaker G(1)(2)(3)(5).

Author information:
(1)CSF Global, Dhaka, Bangladesh.
(2)Asian Institute of Disability and Development (AIDD), University of South 
Asia, Dhaka, Bangladesh.
(3)Discipline of Child and Adolescent Health, Sydney Medical School, The 
