Association of Household Income With Life Expectancy and Cause-Specific 
Mortality in Norway, 2005-2015.

Kinge JM(1)(2), Modalsli JH(3), Øverland S(1)(4), Gjessing HK(1)(4), Tollånes 
MC(5), Knudsen AK(1)(4), Skirbekk V(1)(6), Strand BH(1)(2)(7)(8), Håberg SE(1), 
Vollset SE(4)(9).

Author information:
(1)Norwegian Institute of Public Health, Oslo, Norway.
(2)University of Oslo, Oslo, Norway.
(3)Statistics Norway, Research Department, Oslo, Norway.
(4)University of Bergen, Bergen, Norway.
(5)Norwegian Organization for Quality Improvement of Laboratory Examinations, 
Bergen, Norway.
(6)Mailman School of Public Health, Columbia University, New York, New York.
(7)Norwegian National Advisory Unit on Aging and Health, Vestfold Hospital 
Trust, Tønsberg, Norway.
(8)Oslo University Hospital, Oslo, Norway.
(9)Department of Health Metrics Sciences and Institute for Health Metrics and 
