An economic evaluation attached to a single-centre, parallel group, unmasked, 
randomized controlled trial of a 3-day intensive social cognitive treatment (can 
do treatment) in patients with relapsing remitting multiple sclerosis and low 
disability.

van Mastrigt GA(1), Evers SM(1)(2), Heerings M(3), Visser LH(4)(5), Ruimschotel 
